astraiea.test.layer2

Class TestLayer2MultiGens

  • java.lang.Object
    • astraiea.test.layer2.TestLayer2MultiGens

  • public class TestLayer2MultiGens
extends java.lang.Object
    JUnit tests for all layer 2 configurations. Carried out by comparing the outcome of carrying out experimentation through layer 2 with the outcome of independently generating data and carrying out experimentation directly through layer 1 (which is known to be correct because it is tested in Layer1JUnit class). If retesting this class Layer1JUnit should also be retested. Layer2Junit assumes that Layer1Junit is correct as it uses Layer1 as an oracle.
    Author:
    Geoffrey Neumann
